# Work Completed

## Agent Identity and Access Management

Created a dedicated read-only account for Mira on Nora.

### Design Goals

* Preserve accountability
* Maintain auditability
* Follow principle of least privilege
* Avoid use of shared administrator credentials

### Access Granted

* SSH access
* Read-only system observation
* Infrastructure inventory collection

### Access Restricted

* sudo
* Docker administration
* libvirt administration
* System modification

This established the first dedicated AI identity within AETHER.

---

## Live Infrastructure Observation

Mira performed an independent inventory of Nora through SSH.

### Information Collected

* Host information
* Operating system details
* Network configuration
* Storage utilization
* Service inventory
* Open ports
* Backup status

### Infrastructure Visibility

Mira successfully identified:

* Docker services
* Cockpit
* SSH
* Backup storage
* DNS configuration
* Running virtual machines through process inspection

### Operational Assessment

Mira correctly identified permission boundaries preventing direct access to:

* Docker
* libvirt

and recommended maintaining those boundaries until additional read-only access requirements are defined.

This represented the first successful AI-driven infrastructure assessment within AETHER.

